---
title: Mexican Crumbed Chicken Burger & Fries with Charred Corn Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: Have you been dreaming of a Mexican-flavoured crumbed chicken burger? Well how about that – so have we! And we promise
you, it tastes even better in real life than we had imagined.
